4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that helps students become web development experts. The course is designed to teach students how to build applications from scratch. With a duration of 18 weeks, students can go from zero to being paid as a Full-Stack Developer. The course covers the most sought-after skills and technologies in the industry and prepares students for a successful career in tech. The program includes classes in Python and JavaScript, algorithm scripting, front-end libraries, API consumption, and more. Students will also develop and present their own project, gaining valuable hands-on experience. No previous coding skills or advanced math are required to enroll in the course. Both English and Spanish options are available for syllabus and content, with live classes taught in the language of the student's campus. Upon completion of the course, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information and to enroll, visit the 4Geeks Academy website. stop